Cam::

She smiled at BlackFang. "OK, I will. But you got to be with me."  
She then turned and walked to the CR chamber door and put her tiny 
hand into the handle. She had to pull hard, but she finally got the 
door wide open. She stood there waving at the bot inside. "Hi there. 
I'm Cam. But you can call me Cam. This is my bestest friend in the 
whole world, Blackfang. We want to know if you want to stay and play 
with us. Or just stay with us. We won't worry that your a predacon 
since we're maximals." she said still waving with a big smile on her 
little face plates.
